00:38:42.650 --> 00:38:44.930
It means making sure we
have women of color who

00:38:44.930 --> 00:38:47.360
are dramatically
under-represented

00:38:47.360 --> 00:38:49.970
in legislative bodies
around this country.

00:38:49.970 --> 00:38:54.200
That we have transgender
representatives.

00:38:54.200 --> 00:38:56.930
That we have people
from different cultures,

00:38:56.930 --> 00:39:00.260
and religions, and
backgrounds, both

00:39:00.260 --> 00:39:03.230
socioeconomically and otherwise.

00:39:03.230 --> 00:39:07.150
