00:39:38.060 --> 00:39:38.834
a difference.

00:39:38.834 --> 00:39:40.250
Republicans, for
a long time, have

00:39:40.250 --> 00:39:44.300
been very astute at
building from the base up

00:39:44.300 --> 00:39:47.810
and making sure that
they are putting people

00:39:47.810 --> 00:39:50.600
in places where they have
the potential to climb

00:39:50.600 --> 00:39:52.320
in the political world.

00:39:52.320 --> 00:39:55.130
